excerpt.rendered:
The Bullit 540 with M.O.B. certification.
The Bullit 540 outboard with M.O.B. certification is 5.40m long and 2.00m wide. The draft is 0.20m and the vertical clearance 1.15m. The hull weight of the aluminium tender boat is 520 kg.
